question: I've got 10 more days till I'm due but heading into the hospital in 30 mins to be induced. I've had high blood pressure which is very high now, protein in my urine and other preeclampsia symptoms. I've been in the last 2 days, first day I was 1cm and had a sweep. Second day I had another sweep and was 2 cm. I'm very nervous but so excited to met my little girl :) this is my second induction and labor and still freaking out!
title: Very nervous but excited
